name: Terms and Conditions: You hereby grant to us
description: By @sashastiles, from an ongoing series of found poems excised from the labyrinthine Terms and Conditions, User Agreements and Privacy Policies of tech giants - recreated as a tactile archive of digital ephemera. Sasha Stiles is a Pushcart-nominated poet and artist working at the intersection of text and technology. sashastiles.com.
